data.name: label6.Text
data.value: We paired up with specialty food purveyor Regalis Foods to bring real black truffle to select Los Angeles and New York City Shacks for a limited time! Founded by Ian Purkayastha and based in NYC, Regalis is known for providing luxury, tough-to-find products including fresh truffles, rare foraged edibles, Japanese wagyu beef, caviar, uni, and live exotic seafoods.
